data.title: Ancient Ports
data.meta_description: Ancient Ports - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a database of nearly 5,000 ancient ports and harbors from around the Mediterranean region. It includes information on the ports' names, modern locations, countries, coordinates, dates of establishment, and whether they were Minoan, Mycenaean, Phoenician, or had remains visible today. The database is based on studies of ancient literature and modern scholarship on ancient seafaring civilizations. It aims to catalog ancient ports and potential anchorages mentioned in ancient sources or identified through modern analysis.
